install node
    brew install node

install npm
    curl http://npmjs.org/install.sh | sh

install jsdom
    npm install jsdom

chmod +x hn.js

install cron (http://benr75.com/pages/using_crontab_mac_os_x_unix_linux)
    - crontab -e
    - 0 */12 * * * /Users/chunghe/dev/google.code/project/hacker-news/hn.js > /dev/null 2>&1
      means run every 12 hours

